(KENARI CHILDREN SCREAMING)

339
00:24:27,916 --> 00:24:30,333
(KENARI CHILDREN HOWLING)

340
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:33,791
(GROANING)

341
00:24:36,666 --> 00:24:37,708
(BLOWING DARTS)

342
00:24:37,791 --> 00:24:40,000
